element.name: constant phase element
element.description: A virtual element with a constant phase angle. Usually used to represent non-ideal capacitance.

source.reference: G. J. Brug, A. L. G. van den Eeden, M. Sluyters-Rehbach, J. H. Sluyters, J. Electroanal. Chem. Interf. Electrochem. 176, 275 (1984)
